sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant API as model-serving-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>8080/8081/9443 TCP
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>50051/TCP gRPC
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,Client: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment

    User->>K8s: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8s->>Controller: Watch event (InferenceService)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Create Route<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Create KEDA TriggerAuth<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Client->>Route: Inference Request<br/>TLS Edge/Reencrypt

    Note over User,Client: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Gateway Auth

    Dashboard->>API: GET /api/v1/gateways<br/>TLS 1.2+ FIPS / Bearer Token
    API->>K8s: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>User Token (forwarded)
    K8s-->>API: Access Decision
    API->>K8s: List Gateways<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>API: Gateway List
    API-->>Dashboard: Filtered Gateways (JSON)

    Note over User,Client: Flow 3: NIM Account Reconciliation

    User->>K8s: Create NIM Account CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8s->>Controller: Watch event (Account)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>NGC: POST /token (authn.nvidia.com)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / API Key
    NGC-->>Controller: OAuth Token
    Controller->>NGC: GET /models (api.ngc.nvidia.com)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token
    NGC-->>Controller: Model Catalog
    Controller->>K8s: Create ConfigMap (model data)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Create Template (ServingRuntime)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Create Pull Secret (nvcr.io)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Client: Flow 4: Gateway EnvoyFilter + AuthPolicy

    K8s->>Controller: Watch event (Gateway)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Check Kuadrant/Authorino TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Create EnvoyFilter<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Create AuthPolicy<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Note right of Controller: Auth chain established
    Client->>Route: Request via Gateway
    Route->>Authorino: ExtAuthz (gRPC/mTLS)<br/>50051/TCP / Service Identity
    Authorino-->>Route: Auth Decision
    Route-->>Client: Response
